If you would like milk or additional condiments please ask our team when you pick up.', u'Enjoy our premium cold brew coffee in a large 96oz coffee box. If you would like milk or additional condiments please ask our team when you pick up.', u'Our balanced and approachable drip blend. Using hot brewing methods you will find notes of fresh oak, vanilla, caramel, dark chocolate and molasses. Flagstaff is also the secret behind our famous Cold Brew. When steeped for 12 hours in room temperature water, this blend produces a caramel sweetness, soft citric acidity and tones of milk chocolate with a juicy finish.', u'Bluestone Lane signature espresso blend. This is what we use in all our shops. Designed to perfectly complement milk with rich notes of cocoa, clove and honeycomb \u2013 expect a cup that is well-structured and has a creamy, full-bodied mouthfeel.', u'Sourced from the Tarqui region of Huila, Colombia, our El Paraiso Single-Origin has a big citrus acidity with juicy orange notes balanced out by a sugary sweet finish. We\u2019ve carefully roasted this coffee to highlight these characteristics to make an enjoyably balanced & unique espresso.', u'Our blend of Colombian coffee is from the Antioquia region and is decaffeinated using the Swiss Water Process method. Swiss Water removes 99% of the coffees caffeine without using harmful chemical solvents. The end result is a delicious full bodied coffee you can enjoy around the clock. Our Colombian Decaf has notes of Maple, Cocao and Brown Sugar.', '', '', u'1QT Califia Barista Edition Oat Milk. Vegan, Gluten-Free, Kosher, & Dairy-Free and made with whole rolled, gluten free oats grown in North America. This oat milk steams beautifully, perfectly pairs with coffee, and tastes dang-good by itself with no gums or stabilizers.', u'1QT Califia Barista Edition Almond Milk. Vegan, Gluten-Free, Kosher, & Dairy-Free with full-bodied goodness, this milk functions as both a "steamer" and creamer for your daily fix of BL coffee or HUSK granola.']

column6: [u'Gregs House, our everyday blend is smooth, naturally sweet and balanced. Great on its own and delicious with milk as well. Tasting notes: chocolate, cherry + vanilla', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso balanced with steamed milk and a thin layer of foam.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso combined with steamed milk and a generous amount of foam.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso balanced with steamed milk our house-made chocolate and a thin layer of foam. Whipped Cream is optional but either way, our mochas are a sweet treat.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso balanced with steamed milk, our house-made caramel, vanilla and a thin layer of foam. A sweet and decadent beverage that tastes like dessert.', u"We start with our silky smooth, Gregs House blend coffee, then mix Califia Farms almond milk and add a touch of honey for a subtly sweet coffee you're sure to love.", u'We went there, we combine Nutella with our silky smooth Gregs House blend coffee and milk for a pleasingly rich, distinctive cup of coffee.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso balanced with steamed milk and the tiniest micro amount of foam.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso poured over hot water. Topped with a layer of crema, our americanos are smooth and refreshing.', u'Night Vision, our espresso blend delivers a big creamy body and chocolatey sweetness while keeping things interesting with notes of orange and plum. Our espresso is truly one of a kind.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso combined with 2 ounces of steamed milk and a very thin layer of foam. A small drink that packs a real punch.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso topped with a generous dollop of foamed milk. A European classic.', u'This cold weather classic will keep you warm and jolly. Our night vision espresso, your choice of milk, and the sweet touch of maple syrup.', '', u'Our velvety and flavorful Night Vision espresso balanced with your choice of milk.', u"We masterfully combine our cold brew with our house-made salted caramel + creamy oat milk for a drink you won't want to end. Go ahead and treat yourself", u'We start by infusing our cold brew with lavender and touch of honey, then artfully blend it with our new unsweetened hemp milk for a fresh take on your daily cold brew', u"We start with our handcrafted cold brew, then mix Califia Farms almond milk and a touch of honey for a subtly sweet cold brew concoction you're sure to love.", u'We went there - we combine Nutella with our handcrafted cold brew and milk for a pleasingly rich, distinctive cold brew drink.', u"We've combined our handcrafted cold brew with Califia Farms oat milk, cinnamon + vanilla for a drink that is very rock & roll.", u'Our creamy and flavorful Night Vision espresso poured over cold water and finished with ice.', u'Night Vision, our espresso blend delivers a big creamy body and chocolatey sweetness while keeping things interesting with notes of orange and plum. Our espresso is truly one of a kind.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso combined with 2 ounces of milk. A small drink that packs a real punch!', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso balanced with milk, our house-made caramel and vanilla. A sweet and decadent beverage that tastes like dessert.', u'Our creamy and flavorful espresso balanced with milk and our house-made chocolate. Whipped Cream is optional but either way, our mochas are a sweet treat.', u'Luxurious ceremonial grade matcha blended with Califia Farms almond milk. Fun Facts: matcha has more antioxidants than any fruit or vegetable, boosts metabolism and is a natural detox! Contains caffeine \u26fd\ufe0f', u'We combine cold-pressed turmeric and ginger roots with a hint of honey as a base, then steam it with Califia Farms almond milk. Fun facts: turmeric root is said to be a powerful anti-inflammatory + ginger root aids in digestion! Insider tip: add freshly ground black pepper as a topping for an added kick', u"Our house-made chai balanced with steamed milk and a thin layer of foam. It's lightly spiced, subtly sweet and fantastically delicious.", u'De-stress with the smooth combination of our house-made chai, licorice root and Califia Farms oat milk. Fun Fact: licorice root is a powerful adaptogen said to be an excellent antiviral, expectorant and gastrointestinal remedy! Contains caffeine \u26fd\ufe0f', u'Select from a variety of rich and flavorful tea blends, artfully sourced + locally packaged.', u"Our house-made chocolate, balanced with vanilla, steamed milk and a thin layer of foam. Whether to keep you warm on a cold day, or just to warm your heart, you can't miss with our hot chocolate.", u'Your choice of milk, served hot or cold!', u'Luxurious ceremonial grade matcha blended with Califia Farms almond milk served over ice. Fun Facts: matcha has more antioxidants than any fruit or vegetable, boosts metabolism and is a natural detox! Contains caffeine \u26fd\ufe0f', u'We combine cold-pressed turmeric and ginger roots with a hint of honey as a base, then mix with Califia Farms almond milk, served over ice. Fun facts: turmeric root is said to be a powerful anti-inflammatory + ginger root aids in digestion!', u'This ruby red delight of a botanical tea is made with organic hibiscus, organic lemon verbena, organic apple pieces, organic orange peel and organic elderberry for an exotically refreshing caffeine free mood booster!', u"We lovingly brew our black iced tea in small batches for a crisp + bold profile that's kissed with bergamot for a subtle citrus flavor.", u'We take great care brewing our green iced tea by hand for a delicate and complex blend of lemongrass, green tea and jasmine blossom.', u"Our house-made chai balanced with your choice of milk. It's lightly spiced, subtly sweet and fantastically delicious.", u'Saratoga Natural Spring Water, as smooth as it gets.', u'Saratoga Sparkling Spring Water, for when you just need a little carbonation to go along with your hydration.', u'Cage-free eggs cooked to perfection using the French \u201csous-vide\u201d technique, combined with turkey sausage and three mouth watering cheeses: Gruyere + Monterey Jack + Cheddar. Our egg bites are packed with protein, loaded with flavor + super convenient \U0001f3af', u'That\u2019s right, we did it, Egg bites that are 100% plant based! We use the French \u201csous-vide\u201d technique to cook Just Egg combined with peppers, roasted corn, black beans, tomatoes, onions and a vegan creme. The result? Incredible flavor + velvety texture all in a super convenient plant-based package.', u"We combine JUST egg, Beyond Breakfast Sausage, Daiya Cheddar Cheese, breakfast potatoes, freshly diced pepper and onions, paprika and a pinch of salt for a vegan breakfast you won't soon forget!", u'Egg whites scrambled with fresh greens topped with organic turkey bacon and white cheddar cheese served on Ezekiel sprouted grain english muffin', u'Freshly carved Fleur De Li ham with gruyere cheese served on a whole wheat ciabatta.', u"The Deluxe goes plant-based! We've revamped our deluxe breakfast sandwich with Just Egg Folded, Beyond Sausage\xae and Daiya Foods cheddar cheese - all stacked in a delicious, buttery vegan chia seed croissant. You'll never want your breakfast sandwich any other way.", u'A plant-based \U0001f331 breakfast sandwich that is stunningly delicious. We combine Just Egg Folded with Daiya Foods American Cheese and a dash of sriracha, served warm \U0001f525 on an artisan rosemary focaccia roll.', u'For a decadent take on the breakfast sandwich, we combine beef sausage, egg and American cheese on a house-made buttery croissant. Served warm \U0001f525', '', u'We took the classic open-faced toast and spiced it up! Creamy guacamole topped with crushed red pepper and a touch of chili oil, all served on house-made Nordic rye bread. Served warm \U0001f525', u'Organic peanut butter, fresh bananas, honey & crushed walnuts served warm on our house-made Nordic rye bread', u'House-made Nordic rye bread. Served warm \U0001f525', u'Oatmeal using coconut milk as a part of the base is almost too good. We combine steel cut oats with coconut milk for a mouth-watering foundation, then customize with a number of toppings and have some fun.', u'This savory favorite is back! Our cheddar jalapeno scone truly is master class in balance - spicy yet comforting. Ingredients: Flour | Sugar | Baking Soda | Baking Powder | Buttermilk | Cheddar Cheese | Butter | Jalapeno', u'A vibrant take on a classic, our house-made biscotti combines walnuts and chocolate with fresh orange zest for a balanced and refreshing treat. Contains: Flour | Baking Powder | Salt | Sugar | Unsalted Butter | Eggs | Orange Zest | Walnuts | Unsweetened Chocolate', u'Simply stated, our plant-based take on the classic blondie will knock your socks off. We start with baby oats and coconut flour as a base, then add almond butter, almond milk and maple syrup for an amazing texture. We finish it off with flaxseeds, cashews and chocolate chips for added crunch and a burst of nutrients.', u'This pound cake reigns supreme as one of our all-time best sellers! House-made daily with freshly mashed bananas and crunchy walnuts, it does not disappoint.', u'This pound cake is rich and perfectly moist. We combine freshly shaved carrots, diced honey crisp apples, raisins and throw sunflower seeds and come coconut in for good measure.', '', '', u"If you're ready for something special, add this to your cart. Our apple fritter is perfectly rich and filled with freshly chopped honeycrisp apples.", u'So simple, so delicious! Our best-selling bites pairs fresh bananas and peanut butter for an ultra-satisfying snack. Ingredients: banana, peanut butter, almonds, medjool dates, baby oats and semi-sweet chocolate chips', u"Alert \U0001f6a8 This is Greg's go-to bite and it's easy to see why. Peanut butter, nuts and seeds make up the luscious base while the chia seed coating provides a welcome crunch. Ingredients: peanut butter, chia seeds, almonds, cashews, rolled oats, sesame seeds, sunflower seeds, raisins, honey and a touch of vanilla.", u"We doubled down on almonds for a simple, healthy and tasty bite. It only took us 6 ingredients to make a bite that will satisfy your cravings. Ingredients: Justin's almond butter, almonds, cashews, medjool dates, cinnamon and a dash of salt", u'We just needed a buckwheat-based bite! A superfood with a superior crunch that we combined with chocolate and espresso for a snack that is utterly blissful. Ingredients: Buckwheat, chocolate chunks, espresso, rolled oats, coconut, agave and chocolate powder', u"When we say this bar is packed with flavor, we're not kidding. The only way to do it justice is to list all the ingredients... Ingredients: peanut butter, granola, rolled oats, coconut, walnuts, apple, banana, figs, dates, prunes, apricots, peanuts, sesame seeds, sunflower seeds, raisins, oh and house-made date syrup", u'Our house-made chocolate chip cookies are nothing short of divine.', u'This house-made muffin is unrecognizably gluten-free and absolutely delightful. Fresh bananas combined with coconut oil and chocolate chips make this one hard to resist.', u'Our house-made blueberry muffin is crafted to have a light and fluffy base dotted throughout with fresh blueberries for a hint of natural sweetness.', u"Our rice chex treat is absolutely sublime. It has all the flavor you'd expect with none of the gluten.", '', u'Get ready to kiss the sky! Our newest smoothie is made with a\xe7a\xed berry, our new unsweetened hemp milk, peanut butter, blueberries, strawberries and banana. 100% plant-based, 1000% delicious \U0001f92f', u'Beggars CAN be choosers. Get your greens in a smoothie that is refreshingly delicious. We blend spinach, Justins almond butter, Califia Farms almond milk, banana, fresh strawberries, fresh blueberries and Ripple plant-based protein.', u"We blend 4 simple ingredients to make a smoothie that always hits the spot. Peanut butter, banana, Silk Soy milk and Ripple plant-based protein, that's it that's the smoothie.", u'We combine strawberries, blueberries and a banana with fresh-squeezed orange juice for a smoothie that is simply delicious.', u'This shot takes the magical powers of blue algae + probiotics and combine them with lemon, ginger and agave for a balanced and refreshing shot of wellness.', u'This shot gets straight to the point! We combine lemon + ginger + cayenne for a spicy \U0001f336 jolt of detoxification that is supremely satisfying.', u"Our cold-pressed orange juice is a burst of citrusy goodness and all the vitamin-C you'll need", u'The perfect juice to energize your day. We artfully mix cold-pressed apple with lemon + ginger + cayenne for a naturally sweet, yet spicy treat.', u'Our in-house green juice is an absolute powerhouse! We had a hard time picking which vegetables and fruits to choose, so we put them all in this one. Ingredients: Kale, spinach, romaine, celery, cucumber, parsley, apple, lemon + ginger', u'We hand pack our parfaits with Esti Foods creamy strawberry Greek yogurt, our house-made granola, fresh strawberries + blueberries, and our house-made strawberry compote to deliver a healthy, dessert like treat.', u'We hand pack our parfaits with Esti Foods vanilla bean Greek yogurt, our house-made granola, fresh strawberries + blueberries to deliver a creamy and flavorful experience.', u'Our plant-based \U0001f331 take on overnight oats. The mouth-watering combination of rolled oats, medjool dates, shaved coconut, coconut milk, peanuts, cinnamon, maple syrup and our house-made granola is second-to-none.', u'Start your day with the power of overnight oats. A rich and flavorful combination of ingredients that will have you ready to take on the day. Ingredients: Rolled Oats, Esti Foods Vanilla Bean Greek Yogurt, Peanut Butter, Chia Seeds, Milk, Cocoa Powder, Salt, Honey + Vanilla', '', u"Our decadent treat is made with vanilla pudding, organic bananas, sweetened condensed milk, and 'Nilla Wafers.", u'Saratoga Natural Spring Water, as smooth as it gets.', u'Saratoga Sparkling Spring Water, for when you just need a little carbonation to go along with your hydration.', u'Gregs House, our everyday blend is smooth, naturally sweet and balanced. Great on its own and delicious with milk as well. Tasting notes: chocolate, cherry + vanilla', u"This intoxicating blend has a velvety body and robust flavors, a dark roast done right. Great on its own and delicious with milk as well. Tasting notes: baker's chocolate, toasted hazelnut + cola", u'Honey | Grapefruit | Raisin | Chocolate', u'We spared no expense on our decaffeinated coffee. A luxurious blend of coffees decaffeinated using the famed Swiss Water Method. All the flavor, none of the buzz. Tasting Notes: Chocolate + Berries', u'We brew our limited edition coffees one cup at a time, made to order, just for you. We rotate these single origin coffees every couple of months, highlighting coffees that are fresh, unique and special. Notes: honey, melon, toffee Country: Nicaragua Tasting Notes: Honey, melon + toffee Variety: caturra, catuai', u'Our cold brew is all the fuel you need to WFH or WTF you need to get done, and now it comes to you ready to drink. Just throw this in your fridge and pour over ice. NO work required. An IV of caffeine, some might say...', u'Our cold brew is all the fuel you need to WFH or WTF you need to get done. Bags include coarse ground coffee and 2 single-use cold brew filters. Good for ~10 total servings, now you can stay cool at home.', u'Our coffee carriers are filled with 96oz of our Gregs House, thats twelve 8 ounce cups of coffee. We blend spoonful after spoonful of buttery roasted pecans with pure, sweet cream to create a delight like no other.', u'We combine our signature vanilla ice cream with rich fudge and decadent brownie pieces to bring this American original to life.', u'We balance a creamy blend of caramel ice cream and rich caramel swirls with the sweet crunch of chocolaty cone pieces to create a sweet, harmonious bite.', u'Rich, creamy, and totally indulgent. Made from the finest cocoa and pure, sweet cream, our chocolate ice cream is the ultimate experience.', u'Irish Cream infused into our ice cream with rich chocolate brownie pieces and a decadent fudge swirl.', u'For those who relish a taste of something playful, we re-created a childhood treat. We blend chunks of buttery cookie dough and sweet fudge chips with our finest pure vanilla ice cream. Ah, such sweet memories.', u'Pieces of rich, chocolaty cookies are dunked in delicious, creamy vanilla ice cream to satisfy the milk-and-cookies kid in all of us.', u'We roast the finest Brazilian coffee beans and brew them to perfection to bring out their rich, complex flavor. the combination of the brew with our pure, creamy ice cream awakens the senses.', u"Inspired by Latin America's treasured dessert, our dulce de leche ice cream is a delicious combination of caramel and sweet cream, swirled with ribbons of golden caramel.", u'An indulgent blend of smooth chocolate ice cream, buttery fudge ribbons and chocolate wafer cookies', u'We infuse mint essence into a smooth, creamy base and add rich chocolaty chips for the perfect finish to this refreshingly cool treat.', u'Let us take you on a voyage to a tropical island where exotic fruits ripen in the golden sun. We combine pure, sweet cream, tropical pineapple, and delectable coconut flavor for a truly indulgent ice cream experience.', u'Its exotic flavor is the hallmark of this remarkable dessert. roasted pistachio nuts gently mixed with pure sweet cream brings out the best in this pairing.', u'Nutty and creamy is a winning combo. Try these great flavors!', u'Velvety swirls of marshmallow, roasted almonds, and our legendary chocolate ice cream come together in this playful ice cream delight.', u'We soak plump raisins in rum and add pure, sweet cream for a rich, flavorful experience infused with just the right hint of warmth.', u"We introduce sweet summer strawberries to pure cream and other natural ingredients. Because it's brimming with real fruit, the true flavor of our strawberries comes shining through.", u'Vanilla is the essence of elegance and sophistication. This marriage of pure, sweet cream and Madagascar vanilla creates the sweet scent of exotic spice and a distinctive taste that lingers on your tongue.', u'A truly exquisite ice cream inspired by fine chocolate truffles. We begin with pure white chocolate ice cream and swirl in satisfying chunks of chocolaty fudge truffles and a tangy raspberry ribbon.', u'We blended juicy, tropical mangos into a smooth puree to create a refreshing treat with sweet fruit intensity.', u"We blended delicious, ripe raspberries into a smooth puree for this tangy yet sweet fruit sorbet. Because it comes with spicy pepperoni, tempting salami and American cheese. It's all mixed with lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, zesty red onions, olives and lots more. Drizzled with our signature Subway\xae Vinaigrette sauce.", u'Enjoy the simpler things? The Veggie Delite\xae salad is simply delish. A pile of your favorite veggies, finished with the dressing of your choice. Crisp. Delicious. All for you.', u'A delicious veggie patty mixed with lettuce, spinach, ripe tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers, zesty red onions and black olives.', u"As delicious as our sandwiches are, they are even better when paired with the perfect side and drink or even adding a little something extra. column9: [u'The sub that proves great things come in threes. In this case, those three things happen to be crisp bacon, lettuce and juicy tomato. While there\u2019s no scientific way of proving it, this B.L.T might be the most perfect sub in existence.', u'Black Forest Ham Signature Wrap is packed with a double portion of ham packed into a tomato basil wrap with lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers and red onions. Definitely delish.', u"Black Forest Ham sandwich is classic. Just add your own flavor. Oh, and it's one of eight six-inch Fresh Fit\u2122 subs with two servings of crisp veggies on freshly baked bread for under 400 calories.", u"Start your day in a sizzlin' way with bacon, egg, and melty cheese on freshly toasted flatbread (or whatever you like). Pile on your favorite veggies and sauce. Start the day right.", u'Savory bacon. Crisp lettuce. Ripe tomatoes. All mixed with baby spinach, crunchy cucumbers, sweet green peppers, black olives, and zesty red onions.', u"As delicious as our sandwiches are, they are even better when paired with the perfect side and drink or even adding a little something extra. With such a variety to choose from, there's truly something for every taste.", u'']

column6: [u"It's a blend of apple, cucumber, celery, lemon, spinach, kale and parsley. Pressed apples put a sweet spin on this balanced green juice. Green spinach and kale, hydrating cucumber and other leafy veggies are balanced by apples and lemon. A perfect choice for those new to juicing.", u'Add a boost to your Hydration Shot intake with our 2oz. Aloe Vera Hydration Shot. With a light and subtle taste, it\u2019s an easy addition to your daily routine. Simply dilute into any amount of Hydration Shot for an instant hydration enhancer or take it as a straight shot.', u"It's a blend of apple, cucumber, celery, lemon, spinach, ginger, kale and parsley. Need a green juice with a little zing? A touch of ginger adds the perfect amount of pizazz to this balanced green juice made with all the goodness of leafy greens plus apple & lemon.", u'Packed with 15 vitamins and minerals, celery juice aids in digestion, detoxification, and calming inflammation! Add it to part of your feel (really) good daily routine and drink everyday on an empty stomach for maximum benefits.', u'Our most intense & lowest calorie cleanse - you get the maximum results in the minimum amount of time. Upon waking, drink your first juice, and drink your next juice in order every two hours thereafter. This bundle includes: Greens 1, Citrus 1, Greens 2, Greens 1, Greens 3, Vanilla Almond.', u'Simple, clean, and full of green goodness. Purists everywhere can rejoice in this no fruit, clean blend of leafy greens, lemon, and celery.', u'This bundle is packed with 6 Probiotic Shots. Give your tummy some TLC with these tasty and easy-to-drink shots. Made with a combination of probiotics and red cabbage, with sweet apple and a slight kick of ginger.', u"This shot is lemony with a powerful kick from ginger and cayenne. Ginger's spicy goodness contains anti-inflammatory properties that help with circulation, aid in digestion by soothing the stomach and support glowing skin and circulation.", u"It's a blend of strawberries, monk fruit, lemon and basil. At only 20 calories per bottle, this lemonade is a refreshing & light combination of fruity strawberries & a light touch of herbaceous basil.", u"Tastes like ice cream in a bottle, we've heard. This drink has all the deliciousness of a vanilla dream, but it's made with all the goodness of almonds, dates, vanilla extract, and just a pinch of sea salt.", u'Our limited-edition fanny pack is here to go with you on your new year & new journey, whichever direction that may mean. It has an insulated inner compartment that holds up to two juices, and each one is made from ~10 recycled plastic bottles. It also represents the new journey ahead for Pressed - a greater commitment to sustainability and the very first look at our new logo!', u'If you\u2019re new to cleansing, this is the juice cleanse for you. Upon waking, drink your first juice, and drink your next juice in order every two hours thereafter. This bundle includes: Vanilla Almond, Greens 2, Roots 2, Citrus 2, Greens 3, Chocolate Almond.', u'This is our most popular cleanse & perfect for those who want to balance great-tasting juices with high efficiency. Upon waking, drink your first juice, and drink your next juice in order every two hours thereafter. This bundle includes: Greens 2, Citrus 2, Greens 3, Roots 3, Citrus 1, Vanilla Almond.', u'Our most intense & lowest calorie cleanse - you get the maximum results in the minimum amount of time. Upon waking, drink your first juice, and drink your next juice in order every two hours thereafter. This bundle includes: Greens 1, Citrus 1, Greens 2, Greens 1, Greens 3, Vanilla Almond.', u'Recharge and replenish with a regular monthly cleanse that still leaves you feeling satiated. Designed for juice lovers who want to try to incorporate cleanses more regularly into their lives, this routine cleanse includes vitamin-rich celery juice and greens juices along with two smoothies and a citrus juice for the perfect balance of phytonutrients and flavor. This cleanse includes: Celery Juice, Greens 1, Avocado Greens Smoothie, Greens 1, Citrus 1, Chocolate Banana Protein Smoothie', u'Not ready for a full day fast yet or want an easy way to stay light & bright this 2021? This half-day fast includes 4 juices chock full of nutrients plus a Wellness Shot, which packs a spicy punch. Celery Juice Greens 3 Citrus 2 Vanilla Almond Wellness Shot See step-by-step guide below.', u'Not ready for a full day fast yet or want an easy way to stay-on-track? This half-day fast includes 4 of our lowest sugar juices from each category of Greens, Roots, Citrus & Signature Blends, plus a wellness shot, which has ginger, lemon & cayenne. See step-by-step guide below.', u'Make this a part of your daily routine with our 5 juice bundle. Packed with 15 vitamins and minerals, celery juice aids in digestion, detoxification and calming inflammation! Add it to part of your feel (really) good daily routine and drink everyday on an empty stomach for maximum benefits.', u'Choose any 6 juices', u'Choose any 6 shots', u'Sip up summer and save $16.20 when you purchase our variety pack 6 with one Strawberry Basil Lemonade, one Elderberry Lemonade, and two of each new flavor (Mango Turmeric Lemonade and Blackberry Lemonade).', u'Get the best of all the wellness-boosting benefits Pressed shots have to offer with a Variety Shot Bundle. Includes a total of 6 shots: 2 Vitality, 2 Elderberry, 2 Wellness.', u'Whether you\u2019ve got a busy schedule or you\u2019re just not a big veggie fan, getting the nourishment your body craves is not always easy. Sneak more nutrients into your daily routine by drinking one Greens 1 & one Roots 1 between meals each day - two of our vitamin-rich blends. With these two cold-pressed powerhouses at the ready, incorporating high-quality nutrition into your day is easier than ever.', u'Get Pressed\u2019s best & most popular flavors in this 6-pack of juices.', u'Get Pressed\u2019s best & most popular flavors in this 6-pack of shots.', u'"Drink one juice & one shot daily to add more fruits & veggies into your routine. Depending on what you\u2019d like to incorporate more of, choose your juice & shot for the week! "', u"This bundle is packed with 6 Wellness Shots. These shots are lemony with a powerful kick from ginger and cayenne. Ginger's spicy goodness contains anti-inflammatory properties that help with circulation, aid in digestion by soothing the stomach, and support glowing skin and circulation.", u'This bundle is packed with 6 vitality shots. These shots are milder than the wellness shots, sweet and spicy with an earthy aftertaste. Turmeric takes the spotlight here containing a compound called curcumin. Benefit from the anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties of curcumin to relieve joint pain and muscle aches.', u'This bundle is packed with 6 Probiotic Shots. Give your tummy some TLC with these tasty and easy-to-drink shots. A tasty & easy-to-drink combination of probiotics & red cabbage with sweet apple & a light kick of ginger.", u'With a dash of honey, cloves & cinnamon, this wellness shot is made with elderberries, which has been shown to help treat cold & flu symptoms.', u'Red tart cherries. Made with antioxidant-rich tart red cherries, which can help lower inflammation. Tastes like sweet cherry juice with a touch of tartness.']

column9: [u"It's a blend of apple, cucumber, celery, lemon, spinach, kale and parsley. Pressed apples put a sweet spin on this balanced green juice. Green spinach and kale, hydrating cucumber and other leafy veggies are balanced by apples and lemon. A perfect choice for those new to juicing.", u'Our limited-edition fanny pack is here to go with you on your new year & new journey, whichever direction that may mean. It has an insulated inner compartment that holds up to two juices, and each one is made from ~10 recycled plastic bottles. It also represents the new journey ahead for Pressed - a greater commitment to sustainability and the very first look at our new logo!', u'Perk up your morning smoothie routine with this satiating blend of banana, almond butter, oats, natural vanilla flavor, and pea protein paired with the energizing duo of coffee & maca powder.', u"It's a blend of mango, lemon, monk fruit and turmeric. The combination of turmeric with refreshing mango and lemon make this elevated lemonade taste like summer in a bottle. Thanks to the properties of turmeric, naturally sweet mango, and a natural monk fruit sweetener, it\u2019s a happy choice inside and out.", u'Packed with 15 vitamins and minerals, celery juice aids in digestion, detoxification, and calming inflammation! Add it to part of your feel (really) good daily routine and drink everyday on an empty stomach for maximum benefits.', u"It's a blend of cucumber, pineapple, coconut water, lemon and aloe vera. Light, revitalizing and fresh, with just the right amount of sweetness. Reach for Citrus 1 for a smooth & mellow juice you can relax & enjoy. Pineapple and lemon are balanced with hydrating aloe vera water & coconut water.", u"It's a blend of carrot, beet, orange, cucumber, lemon, spinach, kale and parsley. An earthy blend of beets, carrots & leafy greens, lightened up with the citrus taste of orange & lemon!", u"Tastes like ice cream in a bottle, we've heard. This drink has all the deliciousness of a vanilla dream, but it's made with all the goodness of almonds, dates, vanilla extract, and just a pinch of sea salt.", u'With a light and subtle \u201cgreen tea\u201d taste, this 2oz hydration shot is recommended for anyone looking to add a boost to their h2o. Simply dilute into any amount of Hydration Shot for an instant hydration enhancer or take it as a straight shot.']

oak, and fruit flavors with hints of toffee and a soft finish.', u'Hailing from Scotland, this whisky was aged in an ex-bourbon cask for 12 years. Hints of vanilla and oak will reward the palate.', u'Classically smooth with bold dried fruit flavors and hints of sherry, smoke, and spice.', u"Staying true to tradition, this gin has been crafted with the same blend since 1793. It's great over ice, or sip it straight.", u'Crisp and clean in taste with firm juniper and the flavors of fresh citrus fruits, this is a gin made for martinis.', u'Best-selling coconut rum with smooth, natural coconut flavor.', u'Rooted in pirate lore featuring a palate of caramel and spice.', u'Medium bodied amber rum with banana and apricot notes and a vanilla finish.', u'A rum to rouse your blood. Rich and full-bodied with strong flavors of caramel, deep chocolate, and burnt toffee.', u'Notes of wood balanced by fruity sweetness and vanilla with a long aftertaste.', u'Grilled pineapple intertwines with notes of vanilla and spice, giving a clean finish.', u'Bold flavor bursting with notes of tropical fruit and dark spices.', u'Rich caramel and vanilla flavors with a long, complex finish punctuated with red pepper.', u'Aged in American oak whiskey barrels for an oaky, earthy flavor with sweet and spicy notes.', u'Crystal clear and smooth with 100% Weber blue agave.', u'Clear and crisp with a light, sweet agave flavor.', u'This tequila was aged in American white-oak barrels for eight months, leaving the signature of a rich and smooth finish.', u'Notes of pepper and clove and hints of green apple make this perfect for sipping.', u'Vanilla-nosed with a powerful, elegant ripe fruit palate.', u'Dekuyper Triple Sec', u'Comfortingly marrying Irish dairy cream, Irish whiskey, and a chocolate blend.', u'Cream liqueur made with Caribbean rum and a hint of spice, vanilla, and cinnamon.', u'Flavored with peaches and citrus fruit, this liqueur is a perfect mixer.', u'Aromatic and juicy melon flavors complimented by hints of banana and a short finish.', u'Juicy passionfruit and fresh tart cranberries blend with French vodka.', u"Artichoke-based and enhanced by a refreshing blend of 13 botanicals, this distinctive liqueur isn't for the faint of heart.", u'This unique infusion of gin contains herbal botanicals, caramelized orange, and delicate spices.', u'Digestive bitter liqueur containing 27 herbs from four continents.', u'Kept secret since 1845, the recipe for this traditional bitters is composed of 27 herbs, roots, and spices.', u"If you like it strong you've come to the right place. This blast of peppermint will knock your fuzzy socks off. Enjoy.", u'Licorice flavor with notes of anise and a sweet and oily finish.', u'A bitter aperitif with bright red color distilled with herbs and fruit.', u"Absinthe's less-vicious cousin, Pernod has a star anise-flavored base, a touch of sugar, and an easier-to-manage alcohol content.", u'Sweet French liqueur made from elderberries with notes of peach, pear, and grapefruit.', u'Subtly spicy from baby ginger and a touch of sweet vanilla, a ginger liqueur that transports to sophisticated scenes of tropical romance.', u'Soft and sweet almond flavors with hints of marzipan and a smooth finish.', u'Stark and powerful, this liqueur holds its own with its fragrant botanicals and natural green color best consumed ice-cold.']

column6: [u'Hoppy Amber Red Lager - Brooklyn, NY - 5.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Brooklyn Lager is amber-gold in color and displays a firm malt center supported by a refreshing bitterness and floral hop aroma. Caramel malts show in the finish.', u'Lager \u2013 Houston, Texas \u2013 4.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Made with real lemonade, this refreshingly crisp beer with a citrus twist has a delicious balance of tart and sweet, perfect for easy-drinking occasions under the sun.', u'German Style Pilsner - Coney Island, NY - 5.2% ABV - 12oz Can - Mermaid Pilsner is a light-bodied, crisp drinking, nicely hopped lager. A heavy-handed addition of rye malt adds a mild spiciness, which is balanced by a light, fruity, floral hop aroma.', u'IPA - Coney Island, NY - 5.8% ABV - 12oz Can - Huge melon, orange and kiwi flavors, and tropical aromas dominate, but are complemented by a strong melanoidin malt backing, finishing clean with the classic K\xf6lsch \u201csnap.\u201d', u'Gluten Free IPA - Montreal, CA - 6% ABV - 16oz Can - Aromatic nose full of citrus, lemon and floral notes, a crisp and sharp mouthfeel paired with light caramel and hoppy flavors. A flavorful, very flavorful quencher.', u'American IPA - Ithaca, NY - 7.2% ABV - 12oz Bottle - Enjoy the clover honey hue and tropical nose of our celebrated flagship ale. Flower Power is simultaneously punchy and soothing with a big body and a finish that boasts pineapple and grapefruit. ... The hint of apricot gives this beer a pleasant nose and fruity finish.', u'Lager \u2013 St. Louis, MO \u2013 4.2% ABV - 12oz Can - A great tasting golden lager, with lower calories than ULTRA, signature low carbs, and a clean, balanced finish. Pure Gold is brewed with organic rice and barley malt, elevating the quality of the beer while delivering a superior taste.', u'American Adjunct Lager - Milwaukee, WI - 4.6% ABV - 7oz Bottle - A classic American-style lager recognized for its consistently crisp, smooth taste and iconic clear-glass bottle. Miller High Life embraces its rich heritage and is known by its drinkers as an authentic, unpretentious beer.', u'Pilsner - Mexico - 4.4% ABV - 16oz Can - This rich, full-flavored Pilsner-style Lager delivers a crisp, refreshing taste. Well-balanced taste and light hop character with a crisp, clean finish. Modelo Especial is characterized by an orange blossom honey aroma with a hint of herb.', u'Orange Peel & Coriander Wheat Ale - Cooperstown, NY - 5.2% ABV - 16oz Bottle - It is pale straw in color, slightly hazy from the yeast, and topped with a huge white, fluffy head. Witte is pleasantly light on the tongue, balanced between malt and wheat sweetness. Hops and spice with a subtle clove note backed by flavors of lemon and sweet orange give way to a dry, crisp, refreshing finish.', u'Blackberry Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - The black widow is fruit-forward, yet tart, with a tantalizing complexity, made with blackberries and freshly pressed New York apples.', u'Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - Traditional cider that contains no artificial flavors or colors. Very pale in color (like an un-oaked chardonnay). Nicely carbonated, with a good dose of apple crispness and buttery apple pulp.', u'American Adjunct Lager - Milwaukee, TN - 4.6% ABV - 16oz Can - Brewed with a combination of 2 & 6-row malted barley, select cereal grains and American and European hops, Pabst Blue Ribbon is fermented with a proprietary lager yeast. Our unique fermentation and maturation process results in a smooth, full bodied beer with a clean, crisp finish with a fine noble hop aroma.', u'Bohemian Pilsner - Portland, ME - 4.6% ABV - 12oz Can - Fresh Cut is a dry-hopped pilsner. Chinook, Citra and Centennial hops provide aromas of citrus, grass and spice. Though the front palate is loud with IPA qualities, the finish is distinctly pilsner- crisp, dry and extremely refreshing.', u"American IPA - Portland, ME - 7.1%ABV - 12oz Can - This unique India Pale Ale features our favorite hops\u2014Simcoe, Amarillo and Nugget. A generous Amarillo and Simcoe dry hop provide for an assertive, hop-forward nose and front palate. We don't use traditional bittering hops in our IPA, providing nothing but stimulating citrus and floral characteristics.", u'Nut Brown Ale \u2013 England, UK \u2013 5% ABV - 12oz Bottle - It pours a rich mahogany brown color, with a solid beige head that shows good retention. The bouquet opens with enticing aromas of toasted malts, brown bread, caramelized brown sugar and warm hazelnuts. The medium-weight body is full and creamy in feel, with pleasant toasted nut and caramel malt flavors.', u'IPA \u2013 Brooklyn, New York \u2013 6.6% ABV - 12oz Can - The enhanced Sixpoint IPA formulation, first released in the summer of 2014 and uses a blend of new hop strains for a juicy, citrusy, piney hop slashing. It all started with an epic video game marathon back in 2004. Rocking blaze-orange homebrew, we saw the foam rings down the glass like tiger stripes. Thousands of batches and tweaks later, the BENGALI\xae still slashes. Tip in back and let gravity do the work. Game on!', u"Double IPA - Brooklyn, NY - 9.1% ABV - 12oz Can - We remember our first sip of hoppy beer, do you? Nearly spit that $#!^ out. Now we fantasize about this stuff. Thinking about those hop ones...bursting with juice...ripe as all hell...makes you look forward to that first RESIN\xae all day long. Can't wait.", u'Passion Fruit, Mango, Pineapple, Watermelon Kiwi - 5% ABV - 12oz Can - Made with simple ingredients and hints of our favorite fruits. Never made with artificial sweeteners or flavors.', u'Yumberry, Blueberry Mango, Black Raspberry and Strawberry Coconut - Wild Basin, CO - 5% ABV - 12oz Can - We exist to keep you running wild and free from the barriers that get in the way of reaching your destination. To help you along the way, we\u2019re bringing the natural and flavorful bounty of the Wild Basin to you \u2013 invigorating your adventurous spirit.', u'Dry Rose Cider - Sagaponack, NY - 6.9% ABV - 10oz Bottle - Bright shiny rose in color.
